## 🎟️ `POST /api/redeem`

**Description**: Redeems an unclaimed NFT tied to a specific user or product. Validates wallet address and checks allowlist status before returning claimable metadata.

**Request Body**:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "wallet_address": "0x1234...abcd",
  "sku": "PIA-ALPHA-001"
}
}
```  
